dc_title_s: Lotharingiae et Utriusque Alsatiae: in ditiones minores divisarum tractibusque insertis et finitimis circumscriptarum, novissima nitidissima et accuratissima; delineatio per Theodorum Danckerts cum privilegio.
dc_description_s: Relief shown pictorially. Has royal arms of Alsace and Lorraine. 1 map; 48 x 56 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
